FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1777338232
OL,3,CAnas Sarwar challenged to order MPs to
OL,4,Cback inquiry into PM
OL,6,FAhead of the vote, SNP Westminster
OL,7,Fleader Stephen Flynn made clear he and
OL,8,Ffellow SNP MPs would be voting in
OL,9,Ffavour of an inquiry.
OL,11,FHe called on Scottish Labour leader
OL,12,FAnas Sarwar ` who has already called
OL,13,Ffor Sir Keir to resign as Prime
OL,14,FMinister ` to do the same.
OL,16,FIn a letter to Mr Sarwar, the SNP
OL,17,FWestminster leader said that Tuesday's
OL,18,FCommons vote was "an opportunity to
OL,19,Fend Keir Starmer's short and sorry
OL,20,Ftime as Prime Minister".
OL,26,@zD@ROU|D@WO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
