PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1777338232
OL,3,CAnas Sarwar challenged to order MPs to
OL,4,Cback inquiry into PM
OL,6,FThe SNP MP told the Scottish Labour
OL,7,Fchief that it was "therefore also the
OL,8,Fultimate test of your claim that you
OL,9,Fwant him to resign".
OL,11,FIn his letter to Mr Sarwar, the SNP MP
OL,12,Fcontinued: "The test is obvious ` if
OL,13,Fyou truly believe Keir Starmer should
OL,14,Fresign then you must now instruct
OL,15,Fevery single Scottish Labour MP to
OL,16,Fvote for an investigation which will
OL,17,Flikely result in Keir Starmer's
OL,18,Fresignation."
OL,26,@oD@SOUqD@SO]tD@LOUzD@MO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/9
