OL,3,CAnas Sarwar challenged to order MPs to
OL,4,Cback inquiry into PM
OL,6,FTory leader Kemi Badenoch has also
OL,7,Fcalled for Labour MPs to back the
OL,8,Freferral to the Privileges Committee,
OL,9,Finsisting the "Prime Minister misled
OL,10,Fthe House of Commons repeatedly".
OL,12,FSpeaking about Sir Keir, Mrs Badenoch
OL,13,Fadded: "He appointed a national
OL,14,Fsecurity risk and friend of a
OL,15,Fconvicted paedophile to be our
OL,16,Fambassador in Washington, our most
OL,17,Fsensitive diplomatic post."
OL,26,@qD@OOUrD@`O]uD@HOUyD@[O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/9
