OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1777338232
OL,3,CAnas Sarwar challenged to order MPs to
OL,4,Cback inquiry into PM
OL,6,FMr Flynn said the "crucial vote" would
OL,7,F"determine whether Keir Starmer will
OL,8,Fbe investigated by the Committee of
OL,9,FPrivileges for misleading parliament
OL,10,Fand the public over the scandal".
OL,12,FThe SNP MP continued: "The consequence
OL,13,Fof this vote couldn't be clearer or
OL,14,Fmore serious.
OL,16,F"If the Privileges Committee were to
OL,17,Festablish that the House of Commons
OL,18,Fwas indeed misled, the seriousness of
OL,19,Fthat offence would inevitably result
OL,20,Fin the Prime Minister's immediate
OL,21,Fresignation."
OL,26,@nD@SOUnD@`O]oD@AOUrD@`O]tD@WOUxD@AOU}D@
OL,26,AMO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/9
