OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1777338232
OL,3,CAnas Sarwar challenged to order MPs to
OL,4,Cback inquiry into PM
OL,6,FHe said there was a "clear
OL,7,Fcontradiction" between the Prime
OL,8,FMinister and the former Foreign Office
OL,9,Fchief Sir Olly Robbins, saying the one-
OL,10,Ftime senior civil servant had been
OL,11,F"clear that 'pressure' was applied and
OL,12,Fapplied repeatedly" over Lord
OL,13,FMandelson's appointment.
OL,15,FChallenging Mr Sarwar to act, the SNP
OL,16,FWestminster leader told him: "If you
OL,17,Fdon't even have the strength to order
OL,18,Fyour MPs to vote on the future of Keir
OL,19,FStarmer, people won't trust another
OL,20,Fword from you or Scottish Labour.
OL,26,@nD@UOUoD@NO]sD@AOUtD@SO]xD@^OU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
