FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1777338232
OL,3,CAnas Sarwar challenged to order MPs to
OL,4,Cback inquiry into PM
OL,6,F"It is a disgrace that at a time when
OL,7,Fthe UK is facing a cost-of-living
OL,8,Femergency, the Labour government is
OL,9,Fcompletely consumed by the Peter
OL,10,FMandelson scandal and is failing to
OL,11,Flift a finger to help families.
OL,13,F"The only way to lance the boil and
OL,14,Fend this distraction is for Keir
OL,15,FStarmer to quit ` or be forced out.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
