FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30508
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1777338232
OL,3,CAnas Sarwar challenged to order MPs to
OL,4,Cback inquiry into PM
OL,6,F"The Prime Minister should have
OL,7,Fresigned months ago ` and SNP MPs will
OL,8,Fbe voting for the inquiry into Keir
OL,9,FStarmer. The only question is whether
OL,10,Fyou are too weak to order Scottish
OL,11,FLabour MPs to do the same."
OL,13,FScottish Labour MP Gregor Poynton
OL,14,Fsaid: "On May 7 Scotland is voting to
OL,15,Fdecide the future of our NHS, our
OL,16,Fschools and our local communities `
OL,17,Fbut the SNP is obsessing over what is
OL,18,Fgoing on elsewhere.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@[O]vD@GOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/9
